  \cf4 10611. \cf6 0001-Master-Index.md\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10612. \cf6 # BlackRoad Operating Binder\cf5 \
  \cf4 10613. \cf6 ## Purpose\cf5 \
  \cf4 10614. \cf6 This binder is the canonical operating system for BlackRoad governance, structure, finance, compliance,\cf5 \
     \cf6 products, and execution.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10615. \cf6 ## Volume Map\cf5 \
  \cf4 10616. \cf6 01 Constitution | 02 Institution | 03 Products And Markets | 04 Finance And Treasury | 05 Compliance And\cf5 \
     \cf6 Trust | 06 Operations And Execution | 07 Filesystem And Infrastructure\cf5 \
  \cf4 10617. \cf6 ## Canonical Source Rule\cf5 \
  \cf4 10618. \cf6 When duplicate files exist, the binder copy is the canonical control copy after review and naming\cf5 \
     \cf6 normalization.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10619. \cf6 ## Review Status\cf5 \
  \cf4 10620. \cf6 Status: Draft / Owner: Alexa / Last Review: YYYY-MM-DD\cf5 \
  \cf4 10621. \cf6 0005-Change-Log.md\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10622. \cf6 # BlackRoad Change Log\cf5 \
  \cf4 10623. \cf6 ## Entry Format\cf5 \
  \cf4 10624. \cf6 Date | Owner | File | Change Summary | Reason | Approval Status | Follow-Up\cf5 \
  \cf4 10625. \cf6 ## First Entry Example\cf5 \
  \cf4 10626. \cf6 YYYY-MM-DD | Alexa | 0161-Stock-Ledger.xlsx | Created initial ledger | Required for canonical records |\cf5 \
     \cf6 Pending | Verify certificate numbering\cf5 \
  \cf4 10627. \cf6 ## Logging Rule\cf5 \
  \cf4 10628. \cf6 Every structural, legal, ownership, or governance document change should be logged here before or at time\cf5 \
     \cf6 of finalization.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10629. \cf6 ## Review Rule\cf5 \
  \cf4 10630. \cf6 Review this file during annual binder refresh and after major financing, trust, or subsidiary changes.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10631. \cf6 0151-Trust-Summary.md\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10632. \cf6 # Trust Summary\cf5 \
  \cf4 10633. \cf6 ## Trust Identity\cf5 \
  \cf4 10634. \cf6 Trust Name: [Insert exact trust name]\cf5 \
  \cf4 10635. \cf6 Trust Date: [Insert date]\cf5 \
  \cf4 10636. \cf6 Trustee: Alexa Louise Amundson\cf5 \
  \cf4 10637. \cf6 Successor Trustee: [Insert successor trustee]\cf5 \
  \cf4 10638. \cf6 ## Corporate Relationship\cf5 \
  \cf4 10639. \cf6 This trust is intended to hold shares of BlackRoad OS, Inc. at the shareholder level and does not replace\cf5 \
     \cf6 the corporation itself.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10640. \cf6 ## Open Questions\cf5 \
  \cf4 10641. \cf6 0153-Trust-Transfer-Checklist.md\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10642. \cf6 # Trust Transfer Checklist\cf5 \
  \cf4 10643. \cf6 ## Preconditions\cf5 \
  \cf4 10644. \cf6 - Confirm exact legal trust name matches trust documents\cf5 \
  \cf4 10645. \cf6 - Confirm current stock certificate holder name\cf5 \
  \cf4 10646. \cf6 - Confirm transfer restrictions under RSPA and related records\cf5 \
  \cf4 10647. \cf6 ## Transfer Steps\cf5 \
  \cf4 10648. \cf6 - Determine whether board consent is required\cf5 \
  \cf4 10649. \cf6 - Reissue or annotate certificate as needed\cf5 \
  \cf4 10650. \cf6 - Update stock ledger and cap table immediately after transfer\cf5 \
  \cf4 10651. \cf6 0167-Equity-Issuance-Checklist.md\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10652. \cf6 # Equity Issuance Checklist\cf5 \
  \cf4 10653. \cf6 ## Issuance Context\cf5 \
  \cf4 10654. \cf6 Recipient: [Name]\cf5 \
  \cf4 10655. \cf6 Security Type: [Common / Preferred / Restricted Stock / Option]\cf5 \
  \cf4 10656. \cf6 Shares or Units: [Insert amount]\cf5 \
  \cf4 10657. \cf6 ## Required Steps\cf5 \
  \cf4 10658. \cf6 - Board approval adopted\cf5 \
  \cf4 10659. \cf6 - Consideration documented\cf5 \
  \cf4 10660. \cf6 - Ledger and cap table updated\cf5 \
  \cf4 10661. \cf6 0411-Banking-Accounts-Register.md\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10662. \cf6 # Banking Accounts Register\cf5 \
  \cf4 10663. \cf6 ## Purpose\cf5 \
  \cf4 10664. \cf6 Track every bank, brokerage, treasury, and custody relationship used by BlackRoad and its subsidiaries.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10665. \cf6 ## Required Fields\cf5 \
  \cf4 10666. \cf6 Institution | Account Name | Last Four | Entity Owner | Purpose | Authorized Signers | Status | Notes\cf5 \
  \cf4 10667. \cf6 ## Control Rule\cf5 \
  \cf4 10668. \cf6 No account should exist without a linked entity owner, defined purpose, and current signer review.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10669. \cf6 ## Review Cadence\cf5 \
  \cf4 10670. \cf6 Review monthly for active accounts and annually for the full binder.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10671. \cf6 0468-Tax-Calendar.md\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10672. \cf6 # Tax Calendar\cf5 \
  \cf4 10673. \cf6 ## Delaware\cf5 \
  \cf4 10674. \cf6 - Annual report due by March 1\cf5 \
  \cf4 10675. \cf6 - Franchise tax due by March 1\cf5 \
  \cf4 10676. \cf6 ## Minnesota\cf5 \
  \cf4 10677. \cf6 - Annual business renewal due by December 31 if registered\cf5 \
  \cf4 10678. \cf6 - Corporate return timing follows applicable tax-year filing deadlines\cf5 \
  \cf4 10679. \cf6 ## Federal\cf5 \
  \cf4 10680. \cf6 - Form 1120 due according to current IRS corporate filing calendar\cf5 \
  \cf4 10681. \cf6 0561-Annual-Compliance-Checklist.md\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10682. \cf6 # Annual Compliance Checklist\cf5 \
  \cf4 10683. \cf6 ## Parent Good Standing\cf5 \
  \cf4 10684. \cf6 - Confirm Delaware annual report filed\cf5 \
  \cf4 10685. \cf6 - Confirm Delaware franchise tax paid\cf5 \
  \cf4 10686. \cf6 - Confirm registered agent active\cf5 \
  \cf4 10687. \cf6 ## Minnesota\cf5 \
  \cf4 10688. \cf6 - Confirm foreign qualification remains active if required\cf5 \
  \cf4 10689. \cf6 - Confirm annual renewal filed\cf5 \
  \cf4 10690. \cf6 ## Records\cf5 \
  \cf4 10691. \cf6 0007-Document-Register.xlsx\cf5  Filled Text\
  \cf4 10692. \cf6 Workbook Columns\cf5 \
  \cf4 10693. \cf6 Document ID | Canonical Filename | Current Location | Canonical Binder Path | Owner | Status | Last\cf5 \
     \cf6 Reviewed | Notes\cf5 \
  \cf4 10694. \cf6 Status Values\cf5 \
  \cf4 10695. \cf6 Have Local | Have Drive | Missing | Placeholder Created | Needs Review | Canonicalized\cf5 \
  \cf4 10696. \cf6 Purpose Rule\cf5 \
  \cf4 10697. \cf6 Every important legal, tax, governance, treasury, trust, and equity file should appear in this register.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10698. \cf6 Maintenance Rule\cf5 \
  \cf4 10699. \cf6 Update the register whenever a file is moved, renamed, replaced, or designated as canonical.\cf5 \
  \cf4 10700. \cf5 Filled Template Blueprint\
